narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Jacqueline Ejim is a Counselor, Professional provider based in Baltimore, MD. From 2018-02 through 2019-12, this provider received $185K in Medicaid payments across 3K claims serving 1K beneficiaries, billing 3 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 87% of billing is concentrated in 90834 (90834), indicating significant specialization in this service.
Billing stopped in 2019-12, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
